{"tid":914394,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"點睇情侶同居？","createTime":"2018-11-24T08:36:36.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-25T05:28:30.000Z","uid":172085,"like":103,"dislike":45,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"899b639fc3802d19067bb543faf25fb6922099de","tid":914394,"uid":172085,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:36:36.000Z","msg":"呢排見唔少人 拍拖之後就會同居<br />\n<br />\n話就話可以日日見 <br />\n叫做比個機會更了解大家 <br />\n<br />\n但同住耐左 真係唔會悶咩<br />\n而且邊有咁多錢搬出黎住 <br />\n<br />\n加上又未必真係講將來 講結婚<br />\n立立 係一個例子<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n想聽下大家點諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 有實際例子更好<br />\n純討論<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  情侶同居好 <br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  結婚之後先一齊住"},{"pid":"89a79d7b4ed5fa409621c3649619a8a6e05c54d5","tid":914394,"uid":69872,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:38:55.000Z","msg":"留低這串鎖匙"},{"pid":"992b38974430f43245d7e76d5399f8ffdc84c1d5","tid":914394,"uid":218415,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"我係決定左會結婚就開始同居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4247a73dcd5724450b57ca97528d90abed3191ea","tid":914394,"uid":172085,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"992b38974430f43245d7e76d5399f8ffdc84c1d5","tid":914394,"uid":218415,"like":9,"dislike":2,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:40:18.000Z","msg":"我係決定左會結婚就開始同居<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-11-24T08:46:28.000Z","msg":"巴打同女朋友 同居緊？拍左幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/run.gif\" c